  "text": "For the partial dominant pruning algorithm (PDP) in [CITATION_1] , when node 1 is the source, its forward node set is F (1) = {6}, then, F (6) = {2, 9}, F (2) = {7}, F (9) = {3, 4}, F (7) = {8}, F (3) = {8}, F (4) = φ. Therefore, nodes 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8 and 9 forward the packet.",
